title: Non application of sections 355 to 361 of the Law.
content: 361A. The provisions of sections 355 to 361 of the Law shall not apply in relation to shares or debentures, to which the Public Offer and Prospectus Law and/or the Open Ended Undertakings for Collective Investments in Transferable Securities (UCITS) and for Related Matters Law apply. Winding Up Winding up of overseas companies. 2 of 9 of 1968.
